Author: 0kye
Text: I am also an ex tumblr user. I started at 135 went down to 110 and am now 150. Anorexia fucked up my metabolism so much that when I actually started eating I gained back more than I started with. I feel awful. You are not alone and you are not a fake. No one can starve themselves forever, you either have to start eating again which most people do, or you die. There are many many many people who ended up their starting weight or even more than that.
